flowchart TD
    P[Producer] --> Q[(Queue<br/>php-heavy-jobs)]
    Q --> C[Consumer 処理]
    C -->|✓ 成功| OK[ack → Queue から削除]
    C -->|✗ 失敗| R{retry<br/>max_retries 回まで}
    R -->|成功| OK
    R -->|全て失敗| DLQ[(DLQ<br/>php-heavy-jobs-dlq)]

    classDef q fill:#F38020,stroke:#F38020,color:#fff
    classDef ok fill:#2a9d8f,stroke:#1b6b60,color:#fff
    classDef fail fill:#d62828,stroke:#8f1d1d,color:#fff
    classDef actor fill:#003682,stroke:#003682,color:#fff
    class Q,DLQ q
    class OK ok
    class DLQ fail
    class P,C actor
